        "timestamp": "2021-05-28 09:49:54.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI think there may be an issue with the @Scheduled tasks in PolicyEngineController.java. I met this before but thought it might be just something I was meeting. You can try and configure an initial delay on the scheduled task \"synchronizeAllPolicies\" - this may solve the issue.\n\n@Scheduled(initialDelay = 10000, fixedRate = 300000)\n\ninstead of\n\n@Scheduled(fixedRate = 300000)\n\nThis fixed it for me...",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
